<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Contact – Plateforme Acupuncture</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/site/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="background-image">
    <header>
        <nav role="navigation" aria-label="Menu principal">
            <a href="../index.php">Accueil</a>
            <a href="../index.php?page=patho">Pathologies</a>
            <a href="../index.php?page=contact" aria-current="page">Contact</a>
            <span class="nav-status">
            {% if session.username is defined %}
                <span class="nav-user">Bienvenue, {{ session.username }}</span> |
                <a href="../index.php?page=logout">Déconnexion</a>
            {% else %}
                <a href="../index.php?page=login">Connexion</a> |
                <a href="../index.php?page=signup">Inscription</a>
            {% endif %}
            </span>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main class="container">
        <h1>Contact</h1>
        <p>Pour toute question, suggestion ou demande d'information complémentaire, vous pouvez utiliser le formulaire ci-dessous ou nous écrire à l'adresse&nbsp;: <a href="mailto:contact@acupuncture-plateforme.fr">contact@acupuncture-plateforme.fr</a></p>
        <form method="post" action="#" aria-label="Formulaire de contact" style="max-width:500px;">
            <label for="nom">Nom :</label>
            <input type="text" id="nom" name="nom" required>
            <label for="email">Adresse e-mail :</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
            <label for="message">Message :</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
            <input type="submit" value="Envoyer">
        </form>
    </main>
    <footer>
        © 2025 Plateforme d’acupuncture
    </footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>
